# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP header rules.
#
# - HTML mora da bude no-cache da bi cutover (novi deploy) bio odmah
#   vidljiv klijentima — bundleovani JS/CSS imaju content-hash u imenu
#   pa mogu da budu agresivno keširani.
# - Fontovi/asseti idu sa godinu dana TTL.
# - Osnovne security header-e dodajemo da Lighthouse ne kuka i da
#   smanjimo površinu napada (nema iframe-a, nema referer leak-a).
#
# F.6 PILOT HARDENING (L-1):
#   - Dodato Content-Security-Policy: blokira inline script (osim za
#     vite-plugin-pwa register koji je hash-ovan u build-u), restriktuje
#     connect-src na Supabase + same-origin (Cloudflare Functions).
#   - Dodato Strict-Transport-Security (HSTS) — Cloudflare već forsira
#     HTTPS ali eksplicitan header dozvoljava browser-u da preskoči
#     HTTP→HTTPS redirect za narednu godinu.
#   - Permissions-Policy popravljen: camera=(self) (NE ()) jer modul
#     Lokacije koristi getUserMedia za skeniranje barkoda. Pre ove
#     izmene, Chrome je blokirao kameru u skenerima — production bug.

/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://*.supabase.co; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co wss://*.supabase.co; media-src 'self' blob:; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; object-src 'none'
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(self), microphone=(), geolocation=()

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/legacy/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
